{"tid":2259754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男警長承認普通襲擊罪 案件下月判刑","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T06:14:57.000Z","uid":54800,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5223a8721cbd80dd98994a8146eeb0357843d820","tid":2259754,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"2020-10-27 HKT 12:48<br />\n<br />\n10名休班警員今年4月懷疑違反限聚令，在元朗吃宵夜，期間一名男警長與女同袍爭執並扯對方頭髮。男警長在屯門裁判法院承認一項普通襲擊罪，案件押後至下月10日判刑，以待索取背景及社會服務令報告，被告獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n案情指今年4月19日，10名警員在屏會街食「宵夜」歡送女警蘇伶雅，蘇伶雅向被告梁珏榮敬酒但被拒，<strong>被告皮鞋被紅酒潑中，兩人於是起爭執並發生肢體衝突</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告扯事主頭髮惡意程度低，被紅酒潑中皮鞋下一時情緒失控犯案，他正尋求心理醫生協助，了解做出如此愚蠢的行為的原因。"},{"pid":"34f1623e5e1ad681a208b703df44071b2c8bf82f","tid":2259754,"uid":21279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"10名休班警員今年4月懷疑違反限聚令，在元朗吃宵夜，期間一名男警長與女同袍爭執並扯對方頭髮。男警長在屯門裁判法院承認一項普通襲擊罪，案件押後至下月10日判刑，以待索取背景及社會服務令報告，被告獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n案情指今年4月19日，10名警員在屏會街食「宵夜」歡送女警蘇伶雅，蘇伶雅向被告梁珏榮敬酒但被拒，被告皮鞋被紅酒潑中，兩人於是起爭執並發生肢體衝突。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告扯頭髮惡意程度低，被紅酒潑中皮鞋下一時情緒失控犯案，又曾獲美國執法部門及市民讚揚超過20次，他正尋求心理醫生協助，了解做出如此愚蠢的行為的原因。辯方亦提到，被告會因而因此失去工作，但遭裁判水佳麗質疑「有冇咁嚴重」。辯方又曾指案發時，女警正跌低，被告捉住女警的頭髮以扶著她，控方不同意，辯方其後收回。"},{"pid":"dea879c0d3354acfcfd5912ee37b6797d70e3a29","tid":2259754,"uid":54800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"控方唔落玻璃樽果面去打.....<br />\n分明係放生....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">一名男警長更涉嫌用玻璃樽襲擊女同事</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=388251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388251&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=3140a8f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388251&h=261f4a87\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=388251</a>"},{"pid":"82fd1612f1daf0e07674f789799b63d5a449a289","tid":2259754,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"認罪 白警嚟"},{"pid":"bc0cf6e5042806bf8cfde3858057b143d56c76e1","tid":2259754,"uid":21279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"扶住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3208a9e27b3482a3f8c2a29ba39bb607de6ea1ca","tid":2259754,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"社會寄生蟲"},{"pid":"eec60e32b18b85754a4f9acb708b39d01355fa22","tid":2259754,"uid":22436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"法官口中既暴徒呢條罪判幾多碌"},{"pid":"4c581021efcb80c461493a8ffe4c9d3d5a9d624f","tid":2259754,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c66f4db1db716b8029f3cefb5d7fcf9a443af","tid":2259754,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"情操高尚, 唔使坐"},{"pid":"b19db67af9f2ad97de12a4fd7fb90b96e304d030","tid":2259754,"uid":146791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c2825c0e881debc555754c1e03ecc30ccb6fd3","tid":2259754,"uid":107681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGJaVsM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGJaVsM.jpg&h=e4cefa67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員扶人示意圖"}]}